WEBVTT

00:00.305 --> 00:02.183
This is how the world works.

00:02.539 --> 00:04.497
The sun shines, the grass grows.

00:05.123 --> 00:07.222
Kobe Bryant arrives to practice at three.

00:08.363 --> 00:09.146
The other three.

00:09.833 --> 00:11.205
Chickens bock, bock, bock.

00:11.593 --> 00:12.885
Broccoli can fight cancer.

00:13.079 --> 00:14.347
Rice provides energy.

00:14.609 --> 00:17.170
Kobe eats rice, broccoli, chicken...

00:17.395 --> 00:18.705
...and the world turns.

00:19.013 --> 00:19.923
Earthquakes shake.

00:20.297 --> 00:20.923
Bakers bake.

00:21.382 --> 00:24.259
Kobe Bryant shakes and bakes defenders.

00:24.615 --> 00:26.283
Philosophers ponder existence.

00:26.382 --> 00:27.182
Scholars read.

00:27.501 --> 00:29.970
Kobe Bryant takes everyone to school.

00:30.659 --> 00:32.682
Rain falls, waterfalls dump water.

00:32.852 --> 00:34.181
Kobe owns the bucket.

00:34.841 --> 00:35.749
That bucket.

00:37.083 --> 00:39.120
Snakes are light, low and fast.

00:39.230 --> 00:40.892
Kobe's shoes are like snakes.

00:41.024 --> 00:42.494
Bees sting when threatened.

00:42.678 --> 00:44.887
Kobe Bryant is never threatened.

00:44.997 --> 00:46.221
Best is ahead of better.

00:46.799 --> 00:48.147
The basket is ahead of the ball.

00:48.528 --> 00:50.623
Kobe is light-years ahead of them all.

00:51.115 --> 00:52.242
This is the way it was,...

00:52.374 --> 00:53.357
...this is the way it is,...

00:53.815 --> 00:55.508
...this is the way it will be.

